Applebee's Logo Applebee’s is an American company which develops, franchises, and operates the Applebee’s Neighborhood Grill + Bar restaurant chain. The Applebee’s concept focuses on casual dining, with mainstream American dishes such as salads, chicken, pasta, burgers, and “riblets”. All Applebee’s restaurants feature a bar area and serve alcoholic beverages. Source
